湖北多地告急 16省“一省包一市”支援武汉以外地市。
Hubei many urgent 16 provinces "one province bag one city" supports Wuhan outside the city.
中国青年报。
China Youth Daily.
冰点周刊                      。
Freezing Point Weekly.
