2月7日15时，国务院联防联控机制召开新闻发布会，介绍进一步做好重点地区疫情防控工作、提高收治率治愈率和降低感染率病死率等相关情况。
At 1500 hours on February 7, the Joint Prevention and Control Mechanism of the State Council held a press conference to introduce the prevention and control of epidemic diseases in key regions, improve the cure rate of treatment and reduce the mortality rate of infection.
现在建立了16个省支援武汉以外地市的一一对口支援关系，以一省包一市的方式，全力支持湖北省加强病人的救治工作。
Sixteen provinces and autonomous regions have been established to provide assistance to Wuhan city-by-city, providing full support to Hubei province in strengthening the treatment of patients.
湖北省广水市人民政府网站截图中青报·中青网记者 江山 程盟超 马宇平 尹海月“SOS！！！广水紧急求援！！！”2月5日，湖北省广水市人民政府在官网使用6个感叹号和一个“SOS”发出紧急求援公告。
"SOS!!!!" February 5, Hubei Provincial People's Government of Guangshui City, Hubei Province, using six exclamation marks and "SOS" to issue an urgent appeal for help.
公告说，当地医疗资源极其匮乏，全市仅有两家二甲医院，此外只有乡镇卫生院，新冠肺炎疫情之下，医护人员日夜工作相当疲惫，“面对凶猛疫情难以应对”，急需医疗队、物资等方面支援。
There are only two hospitals in the township hospitals, and only the township hospitals. Under the new crown pneumonia outbreak, medical staff are working day and night, and "facing a severe epidemic is difficult to cope with," requiring urgent medical support, supplies and other support.
这份公告列出了23种医用防护物资、药品等的日需求量。
The notice listed the daily demand for 23 kinds of medical protective materials, medicines, etc.
截至2月6日24时，广水市累计确诊病例279例，死亡2例。
As of 2400 hours on February 6, the city of Guangzhou had 279 confirmed cases and 2 deaths.
在广水市第二人民医院发布的物资需求清单上，医用防护面罩、医用护目镜、雾化机等物资以及洛匹那韦、丙种球蛋白等药品库存量为“0”。
On the list of material requirements issued by the Second People's Hospital in Guangzhou, the quantity of medical protective masks, medical goggles, atomizers and other materials, as well as the quantity of medicines such as Lopinavir and gamma globulin, is "0."
中国青年报·中国青年网此前就此做过报道后，已有外界力量与当地联系捐赠物资事宜。
China Youth Daily China Youth Net had previously reported on the matter, there have been external contacts with the local donation of materials.
广水市疫情防控指挥部物资组相关负责人告诉记者，几乎所有物资都急缺”。
Guangzhou epidemic prevention and control command of the relevant material group told reporters that almost all materials are in urgent need.
他向中国青年报·中国青年网记者提供的急需物品清单上，列明需要防护服1万套、N95口罩1万只、外科口罩12万只、阿比多尔2500盒、洛匹那韦5500盒等，按日需求量计算，这是10日所需。
The list of urgently needed items he provided to China Youth Daily's China Youth Net reporter included 10,000 suits of protective clothing, 10,000 N95 masks, 120,000 surgical masks, 2,500 boxes of Abidor and 5,500 boxes of Lopinavir, which were needed on a daily basis for 10 days.
这位负责人列出紧缺物资后，补充了一句：“我们还缺医疗专家50人，目前医护人员都是超负荷运转。
"We still have a shortage of 50 medical experts," the official added, adding that "medical staff are overstretched.
”截至2月6日傍晚，广水暂无外地医疗队支援。
As of the evening of February 6, Guangshui had no medical support from overseas medical teams.
湖北多地陆续向外界求援。
Hubei many succor succor succor successively from outside.
中国青年报·中国青年网记者分别询问鄂州、天门、孝感等市疫情防控指挥部和医院，得到的反馈均称床位紧张、物资短缺。
China Youth Daily China Youth Net reporters asked Huzhou, Tianmen, filial piety and other cities such as the command and hospital, the feedback reported that beds are tight, material shortages.
天门市第一人民医院物资科工作人员告诉记者，各乡镇卫生院、接收新冠肺炎患者的定点医院都从该院领取物资，“用量很大，每天按计划发放，也有调整”。
Tianmen City First People's Hospital material department staff told reporters that township hospitals, hospitals to receive patients with new crown pneumonia from the hospital to receive supplies, "a large amount of daily scheduled distribution, but also adjusted.
孝感市疫情防控指挥部物资保障组一名工作人员告诉记者，防护物资的调配，根据每个地区每日新增病例数据，按比例配发。
Xiaogan city disease control command material support team staff told reporters that the deployment of protective materials, based on the daily number of new cases in each region, proportionately distributed.
汉川市人民医院负责募捐物资的工作人员凌军说，从大年三十开始，全院1000多人都参与到救治中，“现在是超负荷在运行”。
Ling Jun, a fund-raiser at the Hanchuan People's Hospital, said more than 1,000 people in the hospital had been treated since the New Year's Eve.
同样的问题也存在于孝感市安陆市人民医院。
The same problem exists in the Anlu People's Hospital in Xiaoyan City.
安陆市人民医院一名工作人员介绍，目前缺防护服、N95口罩、防护面罩，更缺专业的医护人员。
A staff member of the Anlu People's Hospital said there was a shortage of protective clothing, N95 masks, face masks and medical professionals.
该院投入一线救治工作的医护人员有400多人，“缺人，缺人，缺人！”鄂州市中心医院负责接收物资捐赠的工作人员告诉记者，目前医院床位供不应求，“康复出院的比较少，进的人都还在排队”。
The hospital has more than 400 doctors and nurses working in front-line care, "short of personnel, short of personnel and short of personnel!" The hospital staff in charge of receiving donations told reporters that there is a shortage of hospital beds, "fewer convalescent and discharged patients are queuing up."
最急缺的是N95口罩、防护服、医用外科口罩。
The most urgent needs are N95 masks, protective clothing and medical surgical masks.
这些物品日消耗量非常大，该院一线医护人员有1400人左右，日均消耗防护服3000多件、医用外科口罩6000多只。
The daily consumption of these items is very large, the hospital's front-line medical staff of about 1,400 people, daily consumption of more than 3,000 protective clothing, more than 6,000 medical surgical masks.
鄂州市另一家定点医院鄂钢医院设备科负责人告诉记者，他们急缺口罩、医用防护服，“都是政府统一调度，自己联系厂商基本供应不了”。
Huzhou another point of the hospital equipment section told reporters, they emergency gap cover, medical protective clothing, "are the government uniform dispatch, their own contact manufacturers can not supply."
2月4日晚，鄂州市疫情防控指挥部发布了一份倡议书，号召全市退休、离职医护人员和个体医务工作者参与疫情防控工作。
On the night of February 4, the Huizhou Provincial Command of Disease Control and Prevention issued a proposal calling on retired and retired medical personnel and individual medical workers to participate in the prevention and control of the epidemic.
“疫情发展迅速，我们的医护人员，尤其是临床一线具有传染病诊疗经验的医护人员严重不足。
"The epidemic is developing rapidly and our medical staff, especially those with first-line clinical experience in infectious disease diagnosis and treatment, are seriously deficient.
如果您年龄在60周岁以下（视身体情况，可适当放宽），身体健康，诚邀您重新回到您熟悉的工作岗位与我们一起并肩战斗！”鄂州市卫健委医政科介绍，倡议书公布后，截至2月6日14时，已有90多人打电话报名，其中年龄最大的是一位69岁的退休影像科医生。
If you are under the age of 60 (suitable relaxation depending on your physical condition) and in good health, you are cordially invited to join us in your familiar job! "As of 1400 hours on February 6, more than 90 people had signed up, the oldest of whom was a 69-year-old retired imaging doctor.
报名者中，有许多从外地返乡探亲人员，还有许多外省人员打电话询问能否加入。
Many of the applicants had returned home from other places to visit their families, and many others from the provinces had called to ask if they could join.
鄂州市卫健委医政科工作人员告诉记者，重点挑选的是呼吸内科、急诊与重症监护方面专业人员，其他报名人员作为候补力量。
Huzhou City Health Commission medical staff told reporters that the focus of the selection is respiratory medicine, emergency care and intensive care professionals, other candidates as a backup.
已有几名报名的医生和护士被安排了工作。
Several registered doctors and nurses have been placed in jobs.
据当地媒体报道，鄂州“小汤山医院”——雷山医院建成后将新增772张床位。
According to local media, Huizhou "Xiaotangshan Hospital" - Lei Shan Hospital will be built after the construction of 772 beds.
鄂州市通过征用宾馆、医院、厂房等场所，首批已建和在建的发热人员集中留观隔离点有32处，床位数731张。
By requisitioning hotels, hospitals and factories, the first batch of calorific personnel built or under construction in Huizhou city has 32 separate spots with 731 beds.
一名鄂州市民告诉记者，他致电鄂州市疫情防控指挥部医疗组咨询，得知雷山医院一期已经开放，还在协调外部医疗队进入。
Huzhou City, a reporter told reporters that he called the Ezhou epidemic control command medical team, learned that the first phase of Lei Shan Hospital has been opened, is also coordinating the entry of external medical teams.
2月6日，北京大学医学部称，当天傍晚，北京大学国际医院的一支20人医疗队已从北京出发，紧急赶赴鄂州支援。
A 20-member medical team from Peking University's international hospital left Beijing for Huizhou province in the evening, the medical department of Peking University said Tuesday.
2月7日15时，国务院联防联控机制召开新闻发布会，介绍进一步做好重点地区疫情防控工作、提高收治率治愈率和降低感染率病死率等相关情况。
At 1500 hours on February 7, the Joint Prevention and Control Mechanism of the State Council held a press conference to introduce the prevention and control of epidemic diseases in key regions, improve the cure rate of treatment and reduce the mortality rate of infection.
现在建立了16个省支援武汉以外地市的一一对口支援关系，以一省包一市的方式，全力支持湖北省加强病人的救治工作。
Sixteen provinces and autonomous regions have been established to provide assistance to Wuhan city-by-city, providing full support to Hubei province in strengthening the treatment of patients.
